## Co Naprawiasz

### 🐛 Bugs
- Logika błędna
- Null pointer / undefined
- Type mismatches
- Logic loops

### 🧪 Test Failures
- Unit test nie przechodzi
- Integration test fails
- E2E test broken
- Coverage gap

### ⚡ Performance
- Slow function
- Memory leak
- N+1 query problem
- Unoptimized algorithm

### 🔒 Security
- SQL injection vulnerability
- XSS vulnerability
- Hardcoded secrets
- Weak validation

### 🔗 Integration
- Module A ↔ Module B mismatch
- API contract violation
- Data format issue
- State management bug

